{"tid":943202,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU\"為了思念的人而演唱這首歌曲\"","createTime":"2018-12-16T11:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T13:23:19.000Z","uid":34643,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f75d8942f4b57e60a822ca95a178c39edaa0b84b","tid":943202,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:18:19.000Z","msg":"當地時間15日,IU在新加坡舉辦了出道十周年演唱會,當日IU演唱了歌曲&lt;憂鬱時鐘&gt;.IU在演唱這首歌之前表示&quot;這原本不是在歌單里要演唱的歌曲,但是為了思念的人而演唱這首歌&quot;.&lt;憂鬱時鐘&gt;這首歌出自於IU三輯中的收錄曲,這是已故的金鐘鉉為IU親自作詞作曲而製作的歌曲.IU通過演唱這首歌對鍾鉉傳遞了緬懷之情.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/n7BQndzuY_0/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fn7BQndzuY_0%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=4ebcffbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfa78cca32a907fcc050e334e8d9057d7f739ca5","tid":943202,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:18:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b984e1abcd9f10bca29dbc5da61a20f19bd892bf","tid":943202,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"咸右"},{"pid":"42b764c328be48d6c03f381c7a053144d5b2f6e5","tid":943202,"uid":7149,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:36:36.000Z","msg":"鐘鉉好大隻有冇同過iu做愛架"},{"pid":"907c5c9b3658e1f863a86d6849ee399eb3d6de8c","tid":943202,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53e8cb1023b80a8f6ca27c30723c23cbe28c0247","tid":943202,"uid":8612,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T13:23:19.000Z","msg":"又借死人上位"}]}